**Defining Attendance Logic**

I've been thinking about the attendance system requirements. The new design needs a roster-style format with checkboxes. I'm also planning to incorporate the 50% attendance requirement from the constitution, perhaps by displaying attendance percentages or using mathematical notation. I'm leaning toward hardcoding a mock roster initially, given the lack of a backend. Now, I will start to implement it.


